1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,250
=Episode 30=

3
00:01:01,439 --> 00:01:02,840
Master! Master.

4
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,100
Take this one. It's faster.

5
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:28,040
Ye Chen is too slippery.

6
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,120
He wasn't at the hospital
we got intel on.

7
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:31,480
They must've moved him.

8
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,904
Ye Chen's injured.
He can't have gotten far.

9
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:34,840
Search the city.

10
00:01:37,562 --> 00:01:41,000
(Earthworm)

11
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:00,840
Everyone.

12
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,840
This safe room

13
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,599
was built

14
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:06,200
when we handed

15
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,680
Ye Chen over to Quan Baohua.

16
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:09,530
Just in case, I had it specially made.

17
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:12,079
There are enough supplies
for three months.

18
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:13,840
Mr. Tang,

19
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,360
thanks.

20
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,120
Everyone,

21
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,240
we need to split up.

22
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:24,400
Aoxue,

23
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,680
guard the villa.

24
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,630
Keep my parents and Wang Daokun safe.

25
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,360
Got it, Madam.

26
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:31,360
Mr. Tang, you and Wang Dongxue,
head back to Dihao.

27
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,919
And Mr. Qin,
send men to secure Qin family.

28
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,719
Post guards everywhere.

29
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,919
The Wu family can't find out
where Ye Chen is.

30
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:40,360
I'll stay here and look after him.

31
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,560
Mr. Hong, stay at the door.

32
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:43,319
Understood.

33
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,159
Also,

34
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,759
we need to book plane tickets.

35
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,990
At the first chance,
we take Ye Chen and leave Jinzhou.

36
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:48,479
Okay.

37
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:49,800
No.

38
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,199
I'm not leaving.

39
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,319
What do you mean?

40
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:54,680
Look at the situation.
You're trying to be tough?

41
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,800
Yeah, Mr. Ye.

42
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,400
Those people are ruthless.

43
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:59,797
Do you have any idea
how worried Churan's been about you?

44
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:03,919
Honey,

45
00:03:04,850 --> 00:03:06,081
I've got a solution.

46
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:11,200
When Mr. Hong mentioned the Twin Devils
of Zhen'nan and their technique,

47
00:03:11,762 --> 00:03:14,222
it reminded me that Mr. Quan
once taught me a formula

48
00:03:14,487 --> 00:03:15,452
to counter it.

49
00:03:15,862 --> 00:03:17,405
Get the herbs right away.

50
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,037
Make a medicinal bath.

51
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,280
Three days in this,

52
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,960
and I should recover a lot.

53
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:22,800
No.

54
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,950
That's too dangerous.

55
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:25,800
Madam Li,

56
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,000
my parents,

57
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:28,800
and now what happened to you.

58
00:03:29,330 --> 00:03:30,080
I can't just leave.

59
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:33,120
Martial Uncle,
you don't need to worry about me.

60
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,080
Just listen to him.

61
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,120
If he were the type to run,

62
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,925
he wouldn't be Ye Chen.

63
00:03:42,687 --> 00:03:45,187
(Huaying Pharma)

64
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,280
Send half the men

65
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,520
to Xijin District.

66
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,560
How are you?

67
00:04:18,770 --> 00:04:19,319
Much better.

68
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,780
I can move my arms and legs now.

69
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,100
Can't fight yet though.

70
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,519
Give it another two days.

71
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:26,560
No rush.

72
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,160
How is it? Feeling better?

73
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,120
The Wu family

74
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,759
attacked all our positions today.

75
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,075
Luckily, Ms. Xiao was prepared.

76
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,000
We held them off.

77
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,519
Come sit down.

78
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,025
I want you to play a game with me.

79
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:22,079
My grandpa and I both want to live.

80
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,262
But if there's no reason left to live,

81
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,510
then what's the point of holding on?

82
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,040
Sometimes, living or dying
isn't up to you.

83
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,120
That depends
on how determined someone is.

84
00:05:43,975 --> 00:05:45,600
The best part of a game

85
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,800
is when the person playing it with me

86
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,439
enjoys it too.

87
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,160
I have my limits.

88
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:56,199
Your limits matter?

89
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:59,279
What matters is
that you don't break my rules.

90
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,120
Got it?

91
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,079
When people are pushed,

92
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,120
they'll do whatever it takes
to protect themselves.

93
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:11,560
If you insist on playing your game,

94
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,319
I promise

95
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,399
I won't be the only one who gets hurt.

96
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,480
Are you kidding me?

97
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,399
Don't believe me? Try it.

98
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,079
Fine. Let's play.

99
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,959
Mr. Wu, stop messing around.

100
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,439
They're short on men.

101
00:06:31,587 --> 00:06:33,000
They won't hold out much longer.

102
00:06:40,759 --> 00:06:41,560
Just you wait.

103
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:45,275
I'll make you play by my rules.

104
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,360
Grandpa!

105
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,079
Ting,

106
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,879
you've been through a lot.

107
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:19,500
I thought pretending to be sick

108
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,720
and playing the fool
would protect the Song family.

109
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,560
I never imagined

110
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:27,959
my selfishness and cowardice
would end up killing the Ye couple.

111
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,480
In the end, I failed the trust
my old friend placed in me.

112
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,120
Hit them again!

113
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,519
Worthless trash!

114
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:45,240
Leave no one alive!

115
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,839
You wanted to see me?

116
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,879
We're in trouble.

117
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,500
The Wu family's hitting us hard.

118
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,040
We can't hold them off this time.

119
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,279
There's no one left at Qin Gang's place

120
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,360
or Mr. Ye's house.

121
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,759
The reinforcements from Yanjing

122
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,839
won't get here anytime soon.

123
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,319
At this rate,

124
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,120
we can't hold the line.

125
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:08,680
Mr. Wu,

126
00:08:09,290 --> 00:08:10,160
something's not right.

127
00:08:10,687 --> 00:08:11,680
What do you mean?

128
00:08:11,975 --> 00:08:12,860
This is part

129
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:14,920
of Dihao's turf too,

130
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:16,750
but there's nobody guarding it.

131
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,279
Doesn't that seem strange?

132
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,199
They're not idiots.

133
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,360
Tang Sihai and Qin Gang
are both old foxes.

134
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,639
Don't forget the Empty Fort Strategy.

135
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:36,399
You're asking to be found.

136
00:08:36,959 --> 00:08:38,120
Yin Biao, Yin Lu.

137
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,759
You remember me?

138
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,799
Isn't this Mr. Hong?

139
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,320
Alive, huh?

140
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,600
Were you waiting for me
to finish you off myself?

141
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,080
You!

142
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,080
As long as I, Hong Wu, am here,

143
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:51,519
I won't let you move an inch!

144
00:09:29,237 --> 00:09:29,879
Ye Chen.

145
00:09:30,562 --> 00:09:31,639
Stay calm.

146
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:33,519
You won't regain your strength
for another twelve hours.

147
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,679
If you go out now,

148
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:36,000
all your efforts will be wasted.

149
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,190
You'll endanger Mr. Hong.

150
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,440
Ye Chen!

151
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:40,080
Stop hiding like a coward!

152
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,919
Come out!

153
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,320
You let Mr. Hong suffer for you

154
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,840
while you hide and run.

155
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,759
What a weakling.

156
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,840
If you don't come out,

157
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,200
I'll stab him myself!

158
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,000
I knew I couldn't stop you.

159
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,960
Even if it means certain death,

160
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:07,480
you wouldn't just stand by.

161
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,200
I'm coming with you.

162
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:24,960
Ye Chen,

163
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,360
you coward.

164
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:27,790
So you finally show your face.

165
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,679
Boring.

166
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,360
We haven't even had our fun yet.

167
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,240
Sorry, Mr. Hong.

168
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,879
I can't take it anymore.

169
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,159
I've let all your efforts go to waste.

170
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,559
Martial Uncle...

171
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,639
Don't call me that.

172
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,279
If we make it through today,

173
00:10:46,975 --> 00:10:48,437
we're brothers, even if not by blood.

174
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:49,320
Okay.

175
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:50,679
Mr. Hong.

176
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:52,039
Today,

177
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,399
I'll call you my big brother too.

178
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,200
Okay.

179
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:57,919
A martial arts movie?

180
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,919
This is turning into a massacre.

181
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,250
Worst case, we die.

182
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:07,039
With you here?
What's there to be afraid of?

183
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,520
Don't move!

184
00:11:21,530 --> 00:11:22,700
You think you can take me on?

185
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,120
Just you?

186
00:11:24,287 --> 00:11:25,337
You've got a lot of nerve!

187
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:27,350
Screw you!

188
00:11:36,587 --> 00:11:37,148
Ye Chen!

189
00:11:37,148 --> 00:11:37,725
Don't move!

190
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,159
Now, where should I start?

191
00:11:40,612 --> 00:11:42,200
Your eyes are so beautiful.

192
00:11:42,625 --> 00:11:44,720
I guess I'll start with those.

193
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,519
Honey.

194
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,200
Are you okay?

195
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:06,679
I'm fine.

196
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,080
It worked!

197
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,759
Master Quan's prescription worked!

198
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:11,360
That...

199
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:12,799
That's impossible!

200
00:12:14,559 --> 00:12:15,559
I should be thanking you.

201
00:12:16,737 --> 00:12:18,519
If you hadn't insisted
on hurting Churan,

202
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:21,100
if you hadn't pushed me this far,
I never would've succeeded.

203
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,279
Honey.

204
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,320
Get some rest.

205
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,320
Wait for me.

206
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,039
Honey.

207
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:17,759
Honey,

208
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:21,120
you're the person I love most
in the whole world.

209
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,990
If anyone so much as touches
a hair on your head,

210
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,799
I'll make them pay with their life.

211
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:35,200
Don't cry anymore.

212
00:13:37,350 --> 00:13:39,840
When we get back, I want to eat
the osmanthus cakes you make.

213
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,320
As long as you want them,

214
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,919
I'll make them for you every day.

215
00:14:11,812 --> 00:14:13,679
I didn't expect Ye Chen to cripple

216
00:14:14,187 --> 00:14:16,337
the Twin Devils' martial arts.

217
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,879
In just a few days,

218
00:14:18,137 --> 00:14:20,440
his skills have improved like crazy.

219
00:14:21,919 --> 00:14:23,000
The Qin family

220
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:25,360
must have some kind
of special medicinal herbs.

221
00:14:27,159 --> 00:14:29,519
And he's got Tang Sihai,

222
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:33,159
Qin Gang, and Hong Wu backing him up.

223
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:34,759
He's got people

224
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,240
and money.

225
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:38,720
If you want to get close to him,

226
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,790
that might be tough.

227
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:43,080
Dad,

228
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:45,360
didn't you always say

229
00:14:45,562 --> 00:14:46,850
everyone has a weakness?

230
00:14:47,879 --> 00:14:49,159
Ye Chen's a hopeless romantic.

231
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:51,279
Xiao Churan is his weak spot.

232
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,799
As long as I get control of Xiao Churan,

233
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:55,200
I can control him.

234
00:14:56,025 --> 00:14:57,200
Forget getting his data.

235
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:58,480
Taking his life

236
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,200
would be easy.

237
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:03,360
So you already have a plan.

238
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,159
Then get moving.

239
00:15:07,759 --> 00:15:08,399
Understood.

240
00:15:11,879 --> 00:15:13,587
If you handle this well,

241
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:15,279
I might

242
00:15:15,687 --> 00:15:18,960
just trust you with this password case.

243
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:23,240
Dad, it's not important.

244
00:15:24,039 --> 00:15:25,240
What matters is that it's fun.

245
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,120
Fun?

246
00:15:50,112 --> 00:15:52,600
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

247
00:15:52,687 --> 00:15:56,440
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

248
00:15:56,900 --> 00:16:01,837
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

249
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,287
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

250
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:07,280
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

251
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:10,975
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

252
00:16:11,275 --> 00:16:14,287
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

253
00:16:14,487 --> 00:16:17,537
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

254
00:16:17,650 --> 00:16:20,612
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

255
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:24,037
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

256
00:16:24,262 --> 00:16:28,012
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

257
00:16:28,012 --> 00:16:30,875
♪I belong to no one♪

258
00:16:30,937 --> 00:16:34,387
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

259
00:16:34,387 --> 00:16:37,062
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

260
00:16:37,062 --> 00:16:43,400
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
